ating.” “Learn to code in 15 minutes.” “7 Emails you should send every week.” “How to Learn any Language in 3 Months.” They’re needy. They overpromise. And they underdeliver. They always do. This is post about learning Dutch the slow way…","fields":{"slug":"how-to-learn-dutch-the-slow-way"},"frontmatter":{"date":"02 <span> June </span>","title":"Learning Dutch the Slow Way","description":"I am not a polyglot and I do not have a natural predisposition to language learning. In language classroom settings, I'm a middling student. However, over the past year, I have managed to teach myself A2 to B1 level Dutch without attending in-person classes. Here's how.","tags":["education","dutch"],"cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='62'%20height='62'%20viewBox='0%200%2062%2062'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M47%207c-6%201-9%202-12%201-5%200-6%200-12%206l-12%209c-11%205-9%2013%203%2016%204%200%204%200%202%202-5%208%209%2017%2024%2016%207-1%2011-3%2017-9l5-5v-8c0-8%200-8-2-8l-5-2-2-2%204-1c5-2%207-4%204-4v-3l1-7c0-3-1-4-4-4s-8%201-11%203'%20fill='%23d3d3d3'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/54277/clogs-klompen.jpg","srcSet":"/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/230ee/clogs-klompen.jpg 43w,\n/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/cfd15/clogs-klompen.jpg 85w,\n/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/54277/clogs-klompen.jpg 170w,\n/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/b94d5/clogs-klompen.jpg 255w,\n/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/e5947/clogs-klompen.jpg 340w,\n/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/0a3fd/clogs-klompen.jpg 500w","srcWebp":"/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/fca77/clogs-klompen.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/311df/clogs-klompen.webp 43w,\n/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/1a143/clogs-klompen.webp 85w,\n/static/d651d2fe26d1aca36eda4ad4f6a52269/